column2: "Firearm, type not stated.  (Does not include mechanics grease gun or caulking gun.)"
"Knife or cutting instrument - include icepick, screwdriver, ax, etc."
"Blunt object - hammer, club, etc.  Facts must suggest weapon was not hands and/or feet."
"Personal weapons - include beating by hands, feet, and/or other body members or use of teeth."
Narcotics and drugs - includes sleeping pills.
Asphyxiation - include asphyxiation or death by gas.
Other - type of weapon not designated or type unknown.
